line_1: Rolls the rich stream of wide munificence.
line_2: Its bounteous beams still ardent to dispense;

line_1: Ye stately piles of old munificence,
line_2: At once the pride of learning and defence,

line_1: In elder times she woo'd Munificence
line_2: With happier tasks, and less refin'd pretence,
